Package: spiro
Title: Make Animated Spirographs
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "W. Joel",
           family = "Schneider",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "w.joel.schneider@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8393-5316"))
Description: Familiar to those who have spent hours with the classic toy "Spirograph," 
             hypotrochoids and epitrochoids are shapes formed by tracing the path of 
             a pen inside a circle as it rolls around inside or outside another circle.
             With this package, you can create, modify, and animate spirograph-like 
             shapes in the svg format.
